data.description: Welcome to this gorgeous 3-level end unit townhome in Parkview! 3 bedrooms 2 full and 2 half baths that backs to woods. 5" plank maple floors on the main level and carpet on upper and lower levels, custom stairs edges meticulously finished by hand! An open spacious kitchen with Corian counters, stainless steel appliances, beautiful bar, bay window, and a glass slider facing serene wood-filled views. The upper level consists of three bedrooms with one being a primary suite with a bathroom consisting of a double vanity sink, shower and sunken tub. The two bedrooms are nice size, with walk in closet. The other features are full  bathroom and laundry. The lower level boasts 12-foot ceilings and an electric fireplace. Fresh paint. This is an amazing location close to parks and recreation, shopping and dining with quick access  to major commuter routes. This is a must see and will not last long- Come make this your home!
